## Async / Background Processing

### Priority Operations

| Operation | Sync/Async? | Reason |
|-----------|-------------|--------|
| AI/ML API (Gemini, ChatGPT) | вҡЎ **ASYNC** | Latency 1-5s |
| Send Email/SMS | вҡЎ **ASYNC** | SMTP latency |
| Send Notification/Push | вҡЎ **ASYNC** | Unpredictable latency |
| Payment Gateway | вҡЎ **ASYNC** | Callback pattern |
| DB CRUD operations | вң… **SYNC** | Fast, need result immediately |

### Critical: External API Calls = @Async

```java
//  WRONG - Synchronous API call in transaction
@Transactional
public void createBook(...) {
    bookRepository.save(book);
    embeddingService.generateEmbedding(bookId);  // рҹ”ҙ BLOCKS 3-5s!
}

//  CORRECT - Fire-and-forget
@Service
public class BookServiceImpl {

    @Async("embeddingTaskExecutor")
    public void generateEmbeddingAsync(Long bookId) { }

    @Transactional
    public BookResponse createBook(...) {
        bookRepository.save(book);
        bookEmbeddingService.generateEmbeddingAsync(bookId);  //  Non-blocking
        return mapper.toBookResponse(saved);
    }
}
```

### Anti-Patterns

- API call in @Transactional = **FORBIDDEN**
- Self-invocation @Async = **@Async ignored**
- Synchronous payment = **User waits 10s**

### Checklist

- [ ] External API = @Async?
- [ ] Transaction does NOT contain I/O?
- [ ] @Async = void or Future?
- [ ] Has retry + circuit breaker?

